snippet.title: A Shopping Trip to Eklan Tor
snippet.description: This is a prototype I created to test out gameplay for a VR game I'm making. It's called Under a Juniper Sky and is about tea and monsters. This prototype is fully playable and will soon be available to download for free on itch.io. (Like as soon as I make the page on there for it)
